  "title": "IT Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for <u><strong>IT Warehouse Assistant (along woodlands road)</strong></u></p><p>No experience is required. Training will be provided.</p><p><u><strong>Job Description and Requirement</strong></u></p><p>* Picking ,packing and preparing IT product such as peripherals, charging cart, replacement  spare part and others device before / prepare for delivery to school or customer.</p><p>* Test & inspect the devices, accessories and others . (check for defects, (such as screen, external charging cable, and iPad or laptop charging cart ) and report the issue / ensure items meet the specification.</p><p>* To assist in doing some IT installation work when required in school.  <br />* Help to do basic testing and configuration on the device. (training provided)<br />* Help to Maintain the cleanliness and neat of warehouse.<br />* Able to assist administrative support when require.<br />* Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p><p><strong>* Salary: $2300 to $2700</strong></p><p>* Working Hours: 9:00am to 6pm - Monday to Friday</p><p><u><strong>Requirement</strong></u></p><p>* Hardworking , have positive attitude and willing to learn.</p><p>* Able to work independently and physical fit. </p><p>Interested,  please WhatsApp us at 85393279 for more detail. </p><p>Only shortlisted will notify. Thank you.</p>",
